      <h2>What Makes RequireHire Different?</h2>
      <p>Most recruitment approaches rely heavily on resumes, applications, and keyword filters. RequireHire flips the script with an **interview-first** model that prioritizes real skills and direct conversations over paperwork.</p>
      
      <div class="difference-box">
        <h3>Key Differences at a Glance</h3>
        <table>
          <thead>
            <tr>
              <th>Aspect</th>
              <th>Traditional Approach</th>
              <th>RequireHire Approach</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td>Starting Point</td>
              <td>Resume upload & mass applications</td>
              <td>Profile verification + AI-powered interview</td>
            </tr>
