    <section>
      <h2>Core Features of RequireHire</h2>
      <p>RequireHire is built for speed, fairness, and real talent discovery. Here are the standout features:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>AI-Powered Interviews & Skill Scoring</strong> – Get evaluated on real abilities with instant scores and feedback.</li>
        <li><strong>Verified Profiles Only</strong> – Builds trust with recruiters and helps serious candidates stand out.</li>
        <li><strong>Direct HR Access</strong> – Skip endless applications; get noticed and interviewed directly by hiring teams.</li>
        <li><strong>AI Matching & Recommendations</strong> – Smart system connects you to the most relevant opportunities based on skills and preferences.</li>
        <li><strong>Interview-Ready Insights</strong> – Structured summaries and performance highlights make it easy for recruiters to decide quickly.</li>
        <li><strong>Free Mock Interviews & Tools</strong> – Practice with AI, build confidence, and improve before real interviews.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>These features reduce ghosting, cut hiring time dramatically, and give freshers a fair shot based on capability — not just credentials.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="tips-list">
      <h2>Practical Suggestions for Freshers & Job Seekers on RequireHire</h2>
      <p>To maximize your chances in this interview-first world, follow these actionable steps:</p>
      <ol>
        <li><strong>Complete & Verify Your Profile Fully</strong><br>Upload accurate details, skills, and projects. A verified profile gets priority visibility.</li>
        
        <li><strong>Take AI Mock Interviews Seriously</strong><br>Practice multiple times — use the feedback to improve answers, confidence, and clarity. Higher scores = better ranking.</li>
        
        <li><strong>Focus on Demonstrating Skills</strong><br>Highlight projects, tools you’ve used, problem-solving examples, and quick learning ability — not just academics.</li>
        
        <li><strong>Be Active & Responsive</strong><br>Check notifications regularly, respond quickly to interview invites, and keep availability updated for smooth scheduling.</li>
        
        <li><strong>Target Roles That Match Your Strengths</strong><br>Use the platform’s smart matching to apply only to jobs where your skills align — quality over quantity.</li>
        
        <li><strong>Prepare for Direct HR Chats</strong><br>Practice the STAR method (Situation, Task, Action, Result) to explain your abilities clearly and professionally.</li>
        
        <li><strong>Build a Strong Skill Narrative</strong><br>In interviews, show enthusiasm to learn and adapt — recruiters value potential highly for entry-level roles.</li>
      </ol>
      <p><strong>Pro Tip:</strong> Treat every AI mock interview like the real thing. Consistent practice can boost your scores significantly and make you interview-ready faster than most candidates.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Final Advice for 2026</h2>
      <p>RequireHire represents the future of hiring — where interviews happen first, skills speak louder than resumes, and freshers get real opportunities without endless waiting. By focusing on preparation, verification, and strong performance on the platform, you can turn the odds in your favor.</p>
      <p>Join today, get interviewed, and start landing roles based on what you can actually do.</p>
